# eng.timeseries planned package surface
#
# Purpose:
#   coverage, gap, fill, resampling, and confidence-band helpers above the core
#   TimeSeries axis semantics.
#
# Current implementation:
#   TimeSeries statistics, integration, axis metadata, and selected alignment
#   metadata are supported for documented public workflows.
#
# Planned helper vocabulary:
#   check coverage
#   fill missing
#   resample
#   confidence_band
#
# Review contract:
#   start/end, expected count, actual count, missing intervals, max gap,
#   leap-year policy, fill policy, and warnings.
